&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Tucson remains still with a light hearted grin on his muzzle.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; Of course my friend, I was just toying with them, nothing serious.  Now, a
&gt; lot of my skills in combat revolve around balance, poise, focus and most
&gt; important, inner peace.  Such was the teachings of Master Yokitron.  Which I
&gt; really should be continuing.  Mach Kick, you can stay on my back, just be
&gt; sure to hold onto me securely.   I&#39;m going to warm up with some basic
&gt; exercises in balance.  And I think I would like to continue in beast mode. &quot;
&gt;
&gt; He slowly gets up on his hind legs, standing in a near erect position.
&gt; Instead of curling his front legs into his chest, he stretches them out and
&gt; begins his exercises.   A look of serenity comes over his face as his front
&gt; legs work as arms and hands, in a graceful dance of poise and tranquility.
&gt; Slowly, his hind legs and feet begin to move gracefully in unison with his
&gt; upper body.  As his tail moves with his body, a gentile breeze is kicked up
&gt; in it&#39;s wake. He minds his feet and moves carefully around his new friends.
&gt; It was his way of training for battle.  The more he moves the faster his
&gt; arms and legs move as swift taloned hands perform the same functions as they
&gt; were if he were in robot mode.  And then the dance blossoms into an
&gt; impressive display of martial arts as the Silver Dragon performs a stellar
&gt; spin/ revolving kick maneuver.  He lands on his feet without a wobble in his
&gt; legs or ankles.  He turns his head to see if Mach Kick was still on his
&gt; back.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; The reason why I chose to warm up this way is because typically, no one
&gt; expects a transformer to fight that way in alt form.  When I first met
&gt; Master Yokitron, he asked me to do something completely out of the normal
&gt; routine of combat training.  I was an Autobot back then and he asked me to
&gt; remain in vehicle form during the first lesson.  I thought he was kidding
&gt; but he wasn&#39;t. So then he asked me to drive a little down a road that he
&gt; sanctioned for Autobot training.  I went down that road and suddenly, I
&gt; found myself on two wheels instead of four.  I was an SUV at the time and I
&gt; was shocked clear out of my suspension cables when I went up on my left
&gt; front and rear tires.   There was a ramp under me and I did not expect it.
&gt; But then he said that even a bulky vehicle can find balance.  And if a bulky
&gt; vehicle can find balance, so can a dragon.  This is what I&#39;m going to try
&gt; and convey in the battle field.&quot;

&lt;NEW&gt;

There was a nod of comprehension from BIG CONVOY as he watched TUSCON.
&quot;I have heard of your master Yokitron.&quot; He said as he folded his
massive arms over his chest. &quot;I am told his students are well trained
in various styles of fighting including Circuit-Su and Metallikato.&quot;

As BIG talked MACH KICK said, &quot;Hey, I&#39;m still up here ya know!&quot; He
said as held on for dear life as TUSCON continued his training.

&quot;I think Magmatron has some sort of similar training.&quot; BIG CONVOY said
with a frown, sseming to ignore MACH KICK for the moment. &quot;I have seen
him fight once or twice.&quot;

